  "title": "warehouse manager",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Operations Management:</strong> Oversee receiving, warehousing, and distribution, ensuring efficiency and accuracy.</li><li><strong>Inventory Control:</strong> Manage stock, perform inventory reconciliations, and handle data within the system.</li><li><strong>Staff Leadership:</strong> Recruit, train, schedule, and motivate warehouse staff to meet performance goals.</li><li><strong>Safety & Compliance:</strong> Enforce health and safety regulations, maintaining a secure working environment and managing equipment maintenance.</li><li><strong>Logistics & Communication:</strong> Coordinate with suppliers, transporters, and clients to manage deliveries and optimize workflows.</li><li><strong>Space & Resource Optimization:</strong> Develop, review, and adjust warehouse layout and storage strategies for maximum efficiency</li></ul>",
